=======================================================================
PROJECT OVERVIEW
=======================================================================

MRCA (Mining Regulatory Compliance Assistant) is an AI-powered web application 
that provides mining safety guidance through novel Advanced Parallel HybridRAG 
technology. The system implements simultaneous VectorRAG and GraphRAG execution 
with intelligent context fusion for enhanced regulatory compliance assistance.

Technology: Advanced Parallel HybridRAG - Intelligent Fusion System
Domain: Mining Safety and Regulatory Compliance
Framework: FastAPI + Streamlit + Neo4j + OpenAI/Gemini

