DISCLAIMER
=======================================================================

MRCA provides informational guidance based on MSHA regulations and should
not be considered as legal advice. Users should consult with qualified
legal professionals for compliance matters.
The Advanced Parallel HybridRAG - Intelligent Fusion
technology is provided for research and educational purposes.

